{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"eeb144f2-48fb-4b67-ac49-3a3495bccd17","content":"Here are the **3 evaluation performance issues** in this project:\n\n### 1. File I/O Property Function (line 13, `.csproj`)\n```xml\n<BuildNotes>$([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('build-notes.txt'))</BuildNotes>\n```\nReading files via `System.IO.File` during evaluation is expensive — it blocks the evaluation thread with disk I/O. Move this to a target that runs at build time instead.\n\n### 2. Overly Broad Glob Pattern (line 9, `.csproj`)\n```xml\n<AdditionalFiles Include=\"**\\*.*\" Exclude=\"**\\bin\\**;**\\obj\\**\" />\n```\n`**\\*.*` walks the entire directory tree during evaluation. If this tree grows (e.g., `node_modules`, generated files), evaluation time scales linearly. Narrow the glob or add expensive directories to `DefaultItemExcludes`.\n\n### 3. Deep Import Chain (imports/)\n```\nEvalHeavy.csproj → level1.props → level2.props → level3.props\n```\nA 3-level nested import chain. Each import adds file existence checks and XML parsing during evaluation. While 3 levels is moderate, it compounds with the other issues and would be worse at scale. Flatten where possible.\n\n**Priority fix:** The `File::ReadAllText` property function is the most impactful — it introduces synchronous disk I/O on every single evaluation (IDE reload, design-time build, etc.).","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3115f810-fa7b-4281-8f0b-a9e7392696fa","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I have a full picture of the project. Let me analyze the evaluation performance issues:\n\n1. **File I/O property function**: `$([System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('build-notes.txt'))` - reading file contents during evaluation is expensive\n2. **Broad glob pattern**: `**\\*.*` - this will walk the entire directory tree during evaluation\n3. **Deep import chain**: level1.props → level2.props → level3.props - 3 levels deep import chain adds evaluation overhead\n\nLet me provide a concise analysis.","outputTokens":496,"requestId":"5C11:101184:1DD49C8:21B5FED:6A07CA80"},"id":"7b532aef-a3c0-4381-99ef-7e5b3402f1de","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:38:22.118Z","parentId":"8fe7cd03-2e02-4592-8b2b-a4171875dd20"}
